name: Copy of Copy of VSHEET APP QUẢN LÝ GỐC
description: An application for police forces to manage traffic accidents, vehicle registrations, events, daily tasks, automatic reports, coordinated verification requests, and Advisory Document Management (Module 7). It features AI-powered image extraction, formal response document generation adhering to Nghị định 30/2020/NĐ-CP with multiple customizable templates, a professional, modern, and scientific UI with a collapsible sidebar, and now AI-powered comprehensive report generation from all modules.
